    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;॥ छान्दोग्योपनिषत् ॥ 
    &lt;div id=&#34;-%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#-%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Chandogyopnishad 1 
    &lt;div id=&#34;chandogyopnishad-1&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#chandogyopnishad-1&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;॥ अथ छान्दोग्योपनिषत् ॥ &lt;br&gt;
ॐ  आप्यायन्तु ममाङ्गानि वाक्प्राणश्च्क्षुः श्रोत्रमथो बलमिन्द्रियाणि च सर्वाणि । &lt;br&gt;
सर्वं ब्रह्मौपनिषदं माहं ब्रह्म निराकुर्यां मा मा ब्रह्म निराकरोदनिकारणमस्त्वनिकारणं मेऽस्तु । &lt;br&gt;
तदात्मनि निरते य उपनिषत्सु धर्मास्ते मयि सन्तु ते मयि सन्तु ॥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;॥ ॐ शान्तिः शान्तिः शान्तिः ॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Chandogyopnishad 2 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् द्वितीयोऽध्यायः</title>
      <link>/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-2/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-2/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/samskrut/Upanishad.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;छान्दोग्योपनिषत् द्वितीयोऽध्यायः 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%B5%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Chandogyopnishad 2 
    &lt;div id=&#34;chandogyopnishad-2&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#chandogyopnishad-2&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;समस्तस्य खलु साम्न उपासनꣳ साधु यत्खलु साधु &lt;br&gt;
तत्सामेत्याचक्षते   यदसाधु तदसामेति ॥ २.१.१॥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;तदुताप्याहुः साम्नैनमुपागादिति साधुनैनमुपागादित्येव &lt;br&gt;
तदाहुरसाम्नैनमुपागादित्यसाधुनैनमुपगादित्येव &lt;br&gt;
तदाहुः ॥ २.१.२॥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;अथोताप्याहुः साम नो बतेति यत्साधु भवति साधु बतेत्येव &lt;br&gt;
तदाहुरसाम नो बतेति यदसाधु भवत्यसाधु बतेत्येव &lt;br&gt;
तदाहुः ॥ २.१.३॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Chandogyopnishad 3 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् तृतीयोऽध्यायः</title>
      <link>/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-3/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-3/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/samskrut/Upanishad.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;छान्दोग्योपनिषत्  तृतीयोऽध्यायः 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Chandogyopnishad 3 
    &lt;div id=&#34;chandogyopnishad-3&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#chandogyopnishad-3&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;असौ वा आदित्यो देवमधु तस्य द्यौरेव &lt;br&gt;
तिरश्चीनवꣳशोऽन्तरिक्षमपूपो मरीचयः पुत्राः  ॥ ३.१.१॥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;तस्य ये प्राञ्चो रश्मयस्ता एवास्य प्राच्यो मधुनाड्यः । &lt;br&gt;
ऋच एव मधुकृत ऋग्वेद एव पुष्पं ता अमृता &lt;br&gt;
आपस्ता वा एता ऋचः   ॥ ३.१.२॥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;एतमृग्वेदमभ्यतपꣳस्तस्याभितप्तस्य यशस्तेज &lt;br&gt;
इन्द्रियं वीर्यमन्नाद्यꣳरसोऽजायत  ॥ ३.१.३॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Chandogyopnishad 4 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् चतुर्थोऽध्यायः</title>
      <link>/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-4/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-4/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/samskrut/Upanishad.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;छान्दोग्योपनिषत् चतुर्थोऽध्यायः 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4-%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A4%A5%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Chandogyopnishad 4 
    &lt;div id=&#34;chandogyopnishad-4&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#chandogyopnishad-4&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;जानश्रुतिर्ह पौत्रायणः श्रद्धादेयो बहुदायी बहुपाक्य आस &lt;br&gt;
स ह सर्वत आवसथान्मापयांचक्रे सर्वत एव &lt;br&gt;
मेऽन्नमत्स्यन्तीति ॥ ४.१.१॥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;अथ हꣳसा निशायामतिपेतुस्तद्धैवꣳ हꣳ सोहꣳ समभ्युवाद &lt;br&gt;
हो होऽयि भल्लाक्ष भल्लाक्ष जानश्रुतेः पौत्रायणस्य &lt;br&gt;
समं दिवा ज्योतिराततं तन्मा प्रसाङ्क्षी स्तत्त्वा &lt;br&gt;
मा प्रधाक्षीरिति ॥ ४.१.२॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Chandogyopnishad 5 - छान्दोग्योपनिषत् पञ्चमोऽध्यायः</title>
      <link>/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-5/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 May 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <author>hari@dasarpai.com (Dr. Hari Thapliyaal)</author>
      <guid>/samskrutyatra/chandogyopnishad-5/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;figure&gt;
      &lt;img class=&#34;my-0 rounded-md&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;/assets/images/samskrut/Upanishad.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;&#34; /&gt;
      
    &lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;छान्दोग्योपनिषत्  पञ्चमोऽध्यायः 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%9E%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%9E%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%AE%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h1&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Chandogyopnishad 5 
    &lt;div id=&#34;chandogyopnishad-5&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 ltr:-left-6 rtl:-right-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100&#34;&gt;
        &lt;a class=&#34;group-hover:text-primary-300 dark:group-hover:text-neutral-700&#34;
            style=&#34;text-decoration-line: none !important;&#34; href=&#34;#chandogyopnishad-5&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;/span&gt;        
    
&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;यो ह वै ज्येष्ठं च श्रेष्ठं च वेद ज्येष्ठश्च ह वै श्रेष्ठश्च &lt;br&gt;
भवति प्राणो वाव ज्येष्ठश्च श्रेष्ठश्च ॥ ५.१.१॥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;यो ह वै वसिष्ठं वेद वसिष्ठो ह स्वानां भवति वाग्वाव वसिष्ठः ॥ ५.१.२॥&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;यो ह वै प्रतिष्ठां वेद प्रति ह तिष्ठत्यस्मिꣳश्च &lt;br&gt;
लोकेऽमुष्मिꣳश्च चक्षुर्वाव प्रतिष्ठा ॥ ५.१.३॥&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
