&lt;h1 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;छान्दोग्योपनिषत्  षष्ठोऽध्यायः 
    &lt;div id=&#34;%E0%A4%9B%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%A6%E0%A4%97%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AA%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A4--%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%B7%E0%A4%A0%E0%A4%BD%E0%A4%A7%E0%A4%AF%E0%A4%AF&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
